{"title":"用hexo和GitHub Pages搭建博客","slug":"用hexo和GitHub-Pages搭建博客","date":"2021-07-06T12:22:34.000Z","updated":"2021-07-07T06:51:13.371Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/用hexo和GitHub-Pages搭建博客.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":null,"covers":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"简介\"><a href=\"#简介\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"简介\"></a>简介</h2><p><a href=\"https://hexo.io/\">Hexo</a>是一个静态博客框架（生成工具），类似的有Hugo、Gridea、Jekyll等。也就是说你写的markdown文本，根据你的主题，hexo会帮你快速地编译成html网页。</p>\n<p>而<a href=\"https://pages.github.com/\">GitHub Pages</a>是开源社区GitHub的一项免费的静态文件部署服务。用Jekyll在上面部署博客是官方推荐的做法。当然你也可以用它来部署一些其他的静态网页，或者拿它来当网盘也不是不可以，不过<a href=\"https://docs.github.com/cn/github/managing-large-files/working-with-large-files/what-is-my-disk-quota\">GitHub的仓库有容量限制</a>（单仓库建议小于1G，单文件建议小于50M），而且网速也不甚理想。</p>\n<p>我们需要的就是在本地写博客然后生成HTML文件，然后推送到默认名字为<em>username.github.io</em>的GitHub的仓库里，这样我们就能用网址访问到我们的博客了。</p>\n<p>这样部署博客有几个好处</p>\n<blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>不需要维护服务器等琐事</li>\n<li>不需要买服务器和域名，也不需要备案、SSL证书等等东西，完全免费</li>\n<li>也不需要担心sql注入、ddos等安全问题</li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>\n<p>但是相对来说也有些缺点</p>\n<blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>无法支持原生评论，访问量统计，注册登录等功能</li>\n<li>相对来说操作较为繁琐，如果想要自定义一些主题功能的话，需要一定的HTML、css基础</li>\n<li>GitHub在国内访问很慢，而且百度并不会收录GitHub Pages</li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"本地安装\"><a href=\"#本地安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"本地安装\"></a>本地安装</h2><h3 id=\"git\"><a href=\"#git\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"git\"></a>git</h3><p>Windows：直接去git官网下载并安装<a href=\"https://git-scm.com/download/win\">git</a></p>\n<p>Linux(Debian系)：<code>sudo apt-get install git</code></p>\n<p>Linux(Red Hat系)：<code>sudo yum install git</code></p>\n<p>还有一些其他版本的Linux，比如arch:<code>sudo pacman -S git</code></p>\n<p>注意：<a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/index.html#Install-Git\">官方文档此处</a>git的包名写的是git-core，因为早期在Linux的软件包管理里，git这个名字被GNU Interactive Tools这个软件占用了，于是Linus开发的版本控制软件git只能用git-core这个名字。</p>\n<p>后来GNU Interactive Tools这个软件在软件包管理器里名字改成了gnuit，把git这个名字腾了出来，你现在去安装git-core这个软件包的话，很可能找不到（也可能设置了alias）。</p>\n<h3 id=\"安装node-js\"><a href=\"#安装node-js\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装node.js\"></a>安装node.js</h3><p>Windows：直接去官网下载并安装<a href=\"https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/\">node.js</a></p>\n<p>linux(Debian系)：<code>sudo apt-get install nodejs</code></p>\n<p>Linux(Red Hat系)：<code>sudo yum install nodejs</code></p>\n<p>archLinux:<code>sudo pacman -S nodejs</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"安装hexo\"><a href=\"#安装hexo\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装hexo\"></a>安装hexo</h3><p>Windows下建议直接用安装完git后右键菜单里的那个命令行，或者使用vscode</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">added 57 packages, and audited 58 packages <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> 17s</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">11 packages are looking <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> funding</span><br><span class=\"line\">  run `npm fund` <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> details</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">found 0 vulnerabilities</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>查看版本，检测是否安装成功</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo -v</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo-cli: 4.3.0</span><br><span class=\"line\">os: win32 10.0.19041</span><br><span class=\"line\">node: 16.4.2</span><br><span class=\"line\">v8: 9.1.269.36-node.14</span><br><span class=\"line\">uv: 1.41.0</span><br><span class=\"line\">zlib: 1.2.11</span><br><span class=\"line\">brotli: 1.0.9</span><br><span class=\"line\">ares: 1.17.1</span><br><span class=\"line\">modules: 93</span><br><span class=\"line\">nghttp2: 1.42.0</span><br><span class=\"line\">napi: 8</span><br><span class=\"line\">llhttp: 6.0.2</span><br><span class=\"line\">openssl: 1.1.1k+quic</span><br><span class=\"line\">cldr: 39.0</span><br><span class=\"line\">icu: 69.1</span><br><span class=\"line\">tz: 2021a</span><br><span class=\"line\">unicode: 13.0</span><br><span class=\"line\">ngtcp2: 0.1.0-DEV</span><br><span class=\"line\">nghttp3: 0.1.0-DEV</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>然后建立一个文件夹并初始化</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo init &lt;folder&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">$ <span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> &lt;folder&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">$ npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>先建立个文件夹再初始化会出现错误</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mkdir &lt;folder&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo init</span><br><span class=\"line\">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>windows下，如果用cmd或者terminal可能报错</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">PS H:\\myproj\\blog\\hexo&gt; hexo s</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo : 无法加载文件 C:\\Users\\username\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\hexo.ps1，因为在此系统上禁止运行 </span><br><span class=\"line\">脚本。有关详细信息，请参阅 https:/go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=135170 中的 about_Exe </span><br><span class=\"line\">cution_Policies。</span><br><span class=\"line\">所在位置 行:1 字符: 1</span><br><span class=\"line\">+ hexo s</span><br><span class=\"line\">+ ~~~~</span><br><span class=\"line\">    + CategoryInfo          : SecurityError: (:) []，PSSecurityException</span><br><span class=\"line\">    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : UnauthorizedAccess</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>可能是power shell默认阻止了脚本运行，设置一下</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Set-ExecutionPolicy -ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"本地配置\"><a href=\"#本地配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"本地配置\"></a>本地配置</h2><p>主要是在根目录下的<code>_config.yml</code>文件里进行配置，一般用vscode打开修改，当然记事本也没问题。</p>\n<h3 id=\"网站配置\"><a href=\"#网站配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"网站配置\"></a>网站配置</h3><figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Site</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">title:</span> <span class=\"string\">starY的blog</span>\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\"># 网站的标题，会出现在标签页上</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">subtitle:</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#x27;</span>\t\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\"># 副标题</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">description:</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#x27;</span>\t\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\"># 网站描述，供搜索引擎的搜索使用，不过百度不收录GitHub Pages</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">keywords:</span>\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\"># 关键词，供搜索引擎的搜索使用</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">author:</span> <span class=\"string\">starY</span>\t\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\"># 作者</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">language:</span> <span class=\"string\">zh-CN</span>\t\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\"># 网站的使用语言，可以设置成zh-Hans和 zh-CN，不修改可能出现乱码</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">timezone:</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;Asia/Shanghai&#x27;</span>\t<span class=\"comment\"># 网站时区</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"网址配置\"><a href=\"#网址配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"网址配置\"></a>网址配置</h3><figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># URL</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">## Set your site url here. For example, if you use GitHub Page, set url as &#x27;https://username.github.io/project&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">## 网址，如果要用GitHub Pages,请设置成username.github.io</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">url:</span> <span class=\"string\">https://nanostary.github.io</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">permalink:</span> <span class=\"string\">:year/:month/:day/:title/</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">permalink_defaults:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">pretty_urls:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">trailing_index:</span> <span class=\"literal\">true</span> <span class=\"comment\"># Set to false to remove trailing &#x27;index.html&#x27; from permalinks</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">trailing_html:</span> <span class=\"literal\">true</span> <span class=\"comment\"># Set to false to remove trailing &#x27;.html&#x27; from permalinks</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"文章布局\"><a href=\"#文章布局\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"文章布局\"></a>文章布局</h3><figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Writing</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">new_post_name:</span> <span class=\"string\">:title.md</span> <span class=\"comment\"># 文章的名字</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">default_layout:</span> <span class=\"string\">post</span>\t<span class=\"comment\">#预设布局</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">titlecase:</span> <span class=\"literal\">false</span> <span class=\"comment\"># Transform title into titlecase</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">external_link:</span>\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">enable:</span> <span class=\"literal\">true</span> \t<span class=\"comment\"># 是否在新标签页中打开链接，相当于HTML中的 target=&quot;_blank&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">field:</span> <span class=\"string\">site</span> \t<span class=\"comment\"># 对整个网站（site）生效或仅对文章（post）生效</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">exclude:</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#x27;</span>\t<span class=\"comment\"># 需要排除的规则</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">filename_case:</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>\t<span class=\"comment\"># 把文件名称转换为 (1) 小写或 (2) 大写</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">render_drafts:</span> <span class=\"literal\">false</span>\t<span class=\"comment\"># 显示草稿</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">post_asset_folder:</span> <span class=\"literal\">false</span>\t<span class=\"comment\"># 启动 Asset 文件夹</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">relative_link:</span> <span class=\"literal\">false</span>\t<span class=\"comment\"># 把链接改为与根目录的相对位址</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">future:</span> <span class=\"literal\">true</span>\t\t<span class=\"comment\"># 显示未来的文章</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">highlight:</span>\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\"># 代码块的设置</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">enable:</span> <span class=\"literal\">true</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">line_number:</span> <span class=\"literal\">true</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">auto_detect:</span> <span class=\"literal\">false</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">tab_replace:</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">wrap:</span> <span class=\"literal\">true</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">hljs:</span> <span class=\"literal\">false</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">prismjs:</span>\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\"># 代码块的设置</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">enable:</span> <span class=\"literal\">false</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">preprocess:</span> <span class=\"literal\">true</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">line_number:</span> <span class=\"literal\">true</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">tab_replace:</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"主页设置\"><a href=\"#主页设置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"主页设置\"></a>主页设置</h3><figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Home page setting</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># path: Root path for your blogs index page. (default = &#x27;&#x27;)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># per_page: Posts displayed per page. (0 = disable pagination)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># order_by: Posts order. (Order by date descending by default)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">index_generator:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">path:</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">per_page:</span> <span class=\"number\">10</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">order_by:</span> <span class=\"string\">-date</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"分类和标签\"><a href=\"#分类和标签\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"分类和标签\"></a>分类和标签</h3><figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Category &amp; Tag</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">default_category:</span> <span class=\"string\">uncategorized</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">category_map:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">tag_map:</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"日期时间格式\"><a href=\"#日期时间格式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"日期时间格式\"></a>日期时间格式</h3><p>想要修改的话，参考<a href=\"https://momentjs.com/\">Moment.js</a></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Date / Time format</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">## Hexo uses Moment.js to parse and display date</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">## You can customize the date format as defined in</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">## http://momentjs.com/docs/#/displaying/format/</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">date_format:</span> <span class=\"string\">YYYY-MM-DD</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">time_format:</span> <span class=\"string\">HH:mm:ss</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">## updated_option supports &#x27;mtime&#x27;, &#x27;date&#x27;, &#x27;empty&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">updated_option:</span> <span class=\"string\">&#x27;mtime&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"分页\"><a href=\"#分页\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"分页\"></a>分页</h3><figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Pagination</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">## Set per_page to 0 to disable pagination</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">per_page:</span> <span class=\"number\">10</span>\t<span class=\"comment\"># 每页显示的文章量 (0 = 关闭分页功能)\t,默认是10</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">pagination_dir:</span> <span class=\"string\">page</span>\t<span class=\"comment\"># 分页目录</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"主题\"><a href=\"#主题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"主题\"></a>主题</h3><p>我们可以去<a href=\"https://hexo.io/themes/\">官网</a>更换一个好看一点的主题</p>\n<p>下载到themes文件夹，然后将theme值改成主题文件夹的名字</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Extensions</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">## Plugins: https://hexo.io/plugins/</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">## Themes: https://hexo.io/themes/</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">theme:</span> </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>在主题文件夹中，可能需要我们修改一些配置，在主题文件夹的<code>_config.yml</code>文件中，一般是一些网页上的链接，比如邮箱、GitHub、头像，背景</p>\n<h2 id=\"本地运行编译指令\"><a href=\"#本地运行编译指令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"本地运行编译指令\"></a>本地运行编译指令</h2><h3 id=\"new\"><a href=\"#new\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"new\"></a>new</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo new [layout] &lt;title&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>新建一篇文章。如果没有设置 <code>layout</code> 的话，默认使用_config.yml中的 <code>default_layout</code> 参数代替。如果标题包含空格的话，请使用引号括起来。</p>\n<p>例如</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo new <span class=\"string\">&quot;第一篇文章&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>在命令行输入<code>hexo help new</code>，会有帮助文档，</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo <span class=\"built_in\">help</span> new</span><br><span class=\"line\">INFO  Validating config</span><br><span class=\"line\">Usage: hexo new [layout] &lt;title&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">Description:</span><br><span class=\"line\">Create a new post.</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">Arguments:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  layout  Post layout. Use post, page, draft or whatever you want.</span><br><span class=\"line\">  title   Post title. Wrap it with quotations to escape.</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">Options:</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 自定义新文章的路径</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  -p, --path     Post path. Customize the path of the post.</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 如果存在同名文章，将其替换</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  -r, --replace  Replace the current post <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> existed.</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 文章的 Slug，作为新文章的文件名和发布后的 URL</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  -s, --slug     Post slug. Customize the URL of the post.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"generate\"><a href=\"#generate\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"generate\"></a>generate</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>生成静态文件，也可以缩写成</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>在命令行输入<code>hexo help g</code>，查看帮助文档</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo <span class=\"built_in\">help</span> g  </span><br><span class=\"line\">INFO  Validating config</span><br><span class=\"line\">Usage: hexo generate </span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">Description:</span><br><span class=\"line\">Generate static files.</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">Options:</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 生成过程中如果发生任何未处理的异常则抛出异常</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  -b, --bail         Raise an error <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> any unhandled exception is thrown during generation</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 最大同时生成文件的数量，默认无限制</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  -c, --concurrency  Maximum number of files to be generated <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> parallel. Default is infinity</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 文件生成后立即部署网站</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  -d, --deploy       Deploy after generated</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 强制重新生成文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Hexo 引入了差分机制，如果 public 目录存在，那么 hexo g 只会重新生成改动的文件。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 使用该参数的效果接近 hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo generate</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  -f, --force        Force regenerate</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 监视文件变动</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  -w, --watch        Watch file changes</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>一般不带参数</p>\n<h3 id=\"server\"><a href=\"#server\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"server\"></a>server</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>可以缩写成</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>在命令行输入<code>hexo help s</code>，查看帮助文档</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo <span class=\"built_in\">help</span> server</span><br><span class=\"line\">INFO  Validating config</span><br><span class=\"line\">Usage: hexo server </span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">Description:</span><br><span class=\"line\">Start the server and watch <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> file changes.</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">Options:</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 覆盖默认服务器IP。默认情况下绑定到所有IP地址。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  -i, --ip            Override the default server IP. Bind to all IP address by default. </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 覆盖默认服务器IP。默认情况下绑定到所有IP地址。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  -l, --<span class=\"built_in\">log</span> [format]  Enable logger. Override <span class=\"built_in\">log</span> format.</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 立即在默认web浏览器中打开服务器url，经常使用</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  -o, --open          Immediately open the server url <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> your default web browser.</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 使用的端口号，默认4000</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  -p, --port          Override the default port.</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 只使用静态文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  -s, --static        Only serve static files.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"deploy\"><a href=\"#deploy\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"deploy\"></a>deploy</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>部署网站，可以缩写成</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"clean\"><a href=\"#clean\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"clean\"></a>clean</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo clean</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>清除缓存文件 (<code>db.json</code>) 和已生成的静态文件 (<code>public</code>)。</p>\n<p>更换主题时常用。</p>\n<h2 id=\"GitHub-Pages部署\"><a href=\"#GitHub-Pages部署\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"GitHub Pages部署\"></a>GitHub Pages部署</h2>","categories":[],"tags":[]}